	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would agree with most of what you said but personally I would concentrate on the qeynos area for the simple reason that once you hit level 5 you can go to Black burrow and rack up the exp and get some good cash and qeynos faction.&nbsp;&nbsp;Qeynos faction esp. preists of life faction is good to get early if you ever plan to do the ageis of life quest later on.  Probably best sheild / back item you can get below level 50.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
