	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hmmm, got to say this makes no sense to me.<br><br>Start a Dwarf Cleric then move to Quenos????&nbsp;&nbsp;Greater Faydark, Crushbone, Butsherblock and Steamfont are all great hunting grounds till level 12 or so.  Skells around the broken Clockwork in Steamfont are increadable xp till level 12, don't agro eachother and can be killed quick.  If you make a Dwarf stay in Fadwere till you can bind, xp will be great.<br><br>At level 12 heading to freeport is ok.  I'd go to North or South Ro instead of the Commons though, more MOB's better loot alot of higher undead to kill.  Befallen is horrible, too many trains, too much of a seperation in MOB levels.  Anyone getting xp on second floor Befallen will get slaughtered on 3d floor and get no xp but alot of agro's on first.  And there is no good loot in Befallen except Bone Chips.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
